        <ontology:hasDescription>The average per capita income (EUR/year) [Province] is 24595.08. The total Gross Value Added (GVA) (EUR million/year) [Province] is 7703.09. The primary sector share of total GVA/year [Province] is 2.88%. The secondary sector share of total GVA/year [Province] is 22.63%. The tertiary sector share of total GVA/year [Province] is 74.50%. The per capita income (EUR/year) [Region] is 23071.73. The total Gross Value Added (GVA) (EUR million/year) [Region] is 13507.25. The primary sector share of total GVA/year [Region] is 2.34%. The secondary sector share of total GVA/year [Region] is 30.69%. The tertiary sector share of total GVA/year [Region] is 66.96%.  </ontology:hasDescription>
    </NamedIndividual>
    


