        <ontology:hasDescription>The total number of bed places (BPs) in tourist accommodations/year in the LAU (Local Administrative Unit) is 53310. The regional (Region) share of total BPs/year is 68.02%. The number of agricultural holdings in the LAU is 1198. The nearest settlement with population over 100000 (km) is 36.4. In this region protected areas are present.  </ontology:hasDescription>
